16 Section 3. Section 85-3-102, MCA, is amended to read:
17 "85-3-102. Standards for research in weather modification control. The department may establish
18 by rule standards and instructions to govern the carrying out of research and development or projects in
19 weather modification and control as it considers necessary or desirable to minimize danger to health, safety,
20 welfare, or property. Research and development or projects in weather modification may address only
21 agricultural purposes, including but not limited to minimizing drought conditions, increasing or decreasing
22 precipitation, and preventing hail."
